{"tid":2191737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人爭民主遊行數百人被捕 跨國國會聯盟聲援","createTime":"2020-09-06T15:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T01:15:53.000Z","uid":337052,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"472c8d598cc18f6f981f499e9e89078681ef3b74","tid":2191737,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:32:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">港人爭民主遊行近百人被捕 跨國國會聯盟聲援</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/09/06 23:10<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者唐佩君布魯塞爾6日專電）香港民眾反對港區國家安全法等發起「906」九龍大遊行，遭到港警強行壓制並至少90人被捕，對此，由10餘國國會議員組成的「對華政策跨國議會聯盟」（IPAC）發聲，呼籲國際社會作出適當反應。<br />\n<br />\n香港民眾在網上發起「906」遊行，主要訴求是反對港區國家安全法、要求恢復舉行立法會選舉，以及反對港府推行與中國大陸恢復通關的健康碼。但香港警方強行壓制這場遊行，並至少拘捕90人。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">對華政策跨國議會聯盟（Inter-Parliamentary Alliance on China, IPAC）在推特發言表示，今天原本是香港舉行立法選舉的日子，但這項權利已被剝奪，反對陣營的候選人更被取消資格，參與活動的許多人士被逮捕，呼籲國際社會對此作出適當反應。<br />\n</span><br />\n今年7月由16個國家加上歐洲議會的國會議員成立「對華政策跨國議會聯盟」（Inter-Parliamentary Alliance on China, IPAC），宗旨是團結各國有志一同的國會議員深層合作，訂定積極因應中華人民共和國的戰略作法。聯盟成員包括美國聯邦參議員盧比歐（Marco Rubio）和梅南德茲（Robert Menendez），以及英國、澳洲、加拿大、瑞士、日本、捷克等國的國會議員。<br />\n<br />\n港府7月底以2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫情嚴峻為由，宣布延遲舉行立法會換屆選舉一年，由今年的9月6日延遲至明年9月5日。<br />\n<br />\n此外，包括荷蘭及比利時等媒體今天也對香港警方逮捕抗議者進行報導；荷蘭廣播基金會新聞網站（NOS）表示，今天香港警方逮捕約90名示威者，激進分子遭受催淚彈襲擊；報導並表示自去年以來，香港逐步擴大針對北京影響力日益擴大的示威遊行。<br />\n<br />\n比利時法語廣播電視台（RTBF）報導，由北京任命的香港行政長官林鄭月娥7月宣布，因疫情關係將立法會選舉延後一年，這激起了反對者的憤怒，上街表達不滿。（編輯：高照芬）1090906<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009060197.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202009060197.aspx&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4tKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=de548ba8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009060197.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n============================================<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">註：依據香港蘋果報導為300人被捕</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5556919be1f080b5537aa047c83a3c1a23470307","tid":2191737,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e108d8c661e612220012f0d3f60e9897997a8a3f","tid":2191737,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"Inter-Parliamentary Alliance on China<br />\n@ipacglobal<br />\nToday Hong Kong should be voting in the #LegCo Elections.<br />\n<br />\nThis right has been denied, alongside the disqualification of opposition candidates and the arrest of many activists and journalists.<br />\n<br />\nWe reiterate our call for a proportionate response from the international community.<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ipacglobal/status/1302554269992783872?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fipacglobal%2Fstatus%2F1302554269992783872%3Fs%3D20&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4tKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=8866ff0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fipacglobal%2Fstatus%2F1302554269992783872%3Fs%3D20&h=3634e943\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ipacglobal/status/1302554269992783872?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"55e17c329820f61e8fe5b57e8e2b29af9a0bd526","tid":2191737,"uid":160963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1a70bbad015d6499f5486daa809eb7c354c14de9","tid":2191737,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55e17c329820f61e8fe5b57e8e2b29af9a0bd526","tid":2191737,"uid":160963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"大家上推文留言"},{"pid":"530b4b100ba7a58ee0db7a06c5660ced09aab784","tid":2191737,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"952f818d025f80f3c59ec00a94549b0c4b744a23","tid":2191737,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:38:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ipacglobal/status/130255